const targetMaterials = ['plastic', 'aluminium', 'polypropylene', 'gold'];
const targetThicknesses = [0.263, 0.47, 0.1, 4.0];
const pulseWidths = [30, 60, 500, 475];
const energies = [2.327, 7.0, 135.27, 2.268];
const spotSizes = [3.3, 4.458, 135.27, 4.427];
const intensities = [6.289E+20, 4.578E+19, 2.152E+19, 2.152E+19];
const powers = [77560000000000, 116700000000000, 4775000000000, 4775000000000];
const cutoffEnergies = [4.8, 8.0, 49.25, 8.2];

const newData = [];

for (let i = 0; i < 25; i++) {
  const targetMaterial = targetMaterials[i % targetMaterials.length];
  const targetThickness = targetThicknesses[i % targetThicknesses.length];
  const pulseWidth = pulseWidths[i % pulseWidths.length];
  const energy = energies[i % energies.length];
  const spotSize = spotSizes[i % spotSizes.length];
  const intensity = intensities[i % intensities.length];
  const power = powers[i % powers.length];
  const cutoffEnergy = cutoffEnergies[i % cutoffEnergies.length];

  const dataPoint = [targetMaterial, targetThickness, pulseWidth, energy, spotSize, intensity, power, cutoffEnergy];
  newData.push(dataPoint);
}

console.log(newData);
